PR DESCRIPTION:
Update to use an annotation to check for permissions on Topics and Connector APIs.

# Linked issue

Resolves: #2275 #2278 

# What kind of change does this PR introduce?

- [ ] Bug fix
- [x] New feature
- [ ] Refactor
- [ ] Docs update
- [ ] CI update

# What is the current behavior?

The checks for permissions are not uniformly applied.

# What is the new behavior?

Add a new permissions annotations that checks the Permissions on every API.

# Other information

N/A
